        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Bless you!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000062_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000062_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "Bless you!\" said the rich man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000064_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000064_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "You must have been dreaming!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000064_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000064_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "See, here are two hundred silver pennies, and that is enough and more than enough for six drops of medicine.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000069_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000069_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "Down the stairs stumped the doctor with Babo at his heels.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000069_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000069_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "There stood the cook waiting for them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000073_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000073_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Very well,\" said the cook, and he counted out the two hundred pennies, and Babo slipped them into his pocket.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000080_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000080_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "And then, besides, how about the fortune you promised me?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000099_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000099_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"I got it for a piece of advice,\" said Babo.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000100_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000100_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "For a piece of advice!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000102_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000102_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"I got it for a piece of advice,\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54016_000112_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54016/5940_54016_000112_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "When Babo came the next morning the king gave him ten chests full of money, and that made the simpleton richer than anybody in all that land.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "One of his neighbours, a lady of quality, had two daughters who were perfect beauties.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "There was nothing then to be seen but parties of pleasure, hunting, fishing, dancing, mirth and feasting. Nobody went to bed, but all passed the night in playing tricks upon each other.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"What,\" said he, \"is not the key of my closet among the rest?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Fail not,\" said Blue Beard, \"to bring it me presently.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"How comes this blood upon the key?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"You must die, Madam,\" said he, \"and that presently.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Sister Anne\" (for that was her name), \"go up I beg you, upon the top of the tower, and look if my brothers are not coming; they promised me that they would come to day, and if you see them, give them a sign to make haste.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Come down quickly,\" cried Blue Beard, \"or I will come up to you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"I see,\" replied sister Anne, \"a great dust that comes this way.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Are they my brothers?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Alas! no, my dear sister, I see a flock of sheep.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"Will you not come down?\" cried Blue Beard.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5940/54613/5940_54613_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5940",
        "content": "\"I see,\" said she, \"two horsemen coming, but they are yet a great way off.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5940_54613_000053_000000",
